Abdomen (
Figs. 119–120
): Yellow on most of syntergite 1+2 and medially on all tergites (forming broad, tapering, straight margined medial vitta); lateral part of tergites, including margin, dark brown with narrow yellow spots, each side minimally with 2 short anterior spots on tergite 3 and 1 on tergite 4 (
